Package codes.algorithms.dataStructures

Class LinkedList<T>

java.lang.Object
codes.algorithms.dataStructures.List<T>
codes.algorithms.dataStructures.LinkedList<T>
Type Parameters:
T - Takes in the type of element of the class.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Queue<T>, Stack<T>
public class LinkedList<T> extends List<T> implements Queue<T>, Stack<T>
Class LinkedList, implements Queue and Stack interface and is used to complete FIFO (First-In-First-Out) technique to add and remove elements and FILO (First-In-Last-Out) technique to add and remove elements.
Author:
Trishit Maji
